title: 120: Our Stories From The Road | Ear Biscuits Ep. 120
description:
Rhett & Link talk road stories from their ongoing Tour of Mythicality including the upside of traveling, some of their favorite sites so far, and Rhett's ongoing palm tree-related altercations with his neighbor on this week's Ear Biscuits.
